name: Achichi @Ignister
desc: If this card is Normal/Special Summoned: You can add 1 Level 4 or lower "@Ignister" monster from your Deck to your hand, except "Achichi @Ignister". At the start of the Damage Step, when a Cyberse monster you control battles: You can banish this card from your GY; destroy your monster. You can only use each effect of "Achichi @Ignister" once per turn.
